# AmmoLang — gapless optimal cycle for AI dispatch
# Runs the full combinatorics rebalance as a pure sequence.

@width 16
@motto no gaps only sequences

par ⊕
  grow scan
  surface collapse depth:8

seq ·
  width 16
  gap fill all
  leaf growth:0001
  leaf prog:canonical:assign
  leaf prog:canonical:loop
  wire band:narrow:0
  wire band:narrow:1
  exec canonical:meta